-seop, Yunjin Kim, Ken Jeong, Lee Byung-hun, Daniel Dae Kim, Liza Koshy","releaseDate":"2026-06-12T00:00:00","runningTime":96,"isDurationUnknown":false,"synopsisShort":"Bo właśnie tak tak tak się wyżej wznieś! W kinach tylko 10-18 czerwca! Domknij Honmoon i zaśpiewaj najlepsze hity z filmu „K-popowe łowczynie demonów” razem z HUNTR/X i Saja Boys. Pełna wersja karaoke hitowego filmu Netflixa w kinach tylko 10-14 czerwca.  Gwiazdy K-popu Rumi, Mira i Zoey w przerwach między koncertami na pełnych stadionach bronią fanów przed nadnaturalnymi zagrożeniami, korzystając ze swoich tajemnych mocy.","filmTitle":" K-popowe łowczynie demonów: Karaoke","hasSessions":true,"hasTrailer":true,"embargoMessage":null,"embargoEndDate":null,"embargoLevel":null,"priceMessage":"Kup bilety online i zapłać mniej!","alternativeCertificate":{"name":null,"description":null,"src":null},"panelImageUrl":"https://www.multikino.pl/-/media/multikino/img/import/34ee585f-6f30-4ce6-8f63-916af8c3117c_k-popowe-owczynie-demonow-karaoke_stills_kpop_demon_hunters_u_0.jpg?rev=c802770152e44654bc2089d2696424f6","filmStatus":1,"trailers":[],"director":"Chris Appelhans, Maggie Kang","distributor":"Gutek Film","movieXchangeCode":"d63a4259-bd52-420d-9e8f-19fbd3a4fd8c","crossCountryMovieXchangeId":"d75b7050-85a3-4551-b79c-77dd0e430f22","originalTitle":"KPop Demon Hunters","showingInCinemas":["0003","0004","0005","0006","0007","0008","0010","0011","0013","0014","0015","0023","0024","0025","0026","0028","0029","0030","0031","0033","0034","0035","0036","0037","0038","0039","0040","0041","0042","0043","0044","0047","0048","0050","0051","0052","0053"],"genres":[],"sessionAttributes":[{"name":"NAPISY","shortName":"NAPISY","value":"NAPISY","description":"NAPISY","attributeType":"Language","color":"","borderGradient":[],"backgroundImageUrl":null,"iconName":null},{"name":"2D","shortName":"2D","value":"2D","description":"","attributeType":"Session","color":"","borderGradient":[],"backgroundImageUrl":null,"iconName":null},{"na